To protect your account, your password has been reset, and you will need to create a new one. For advice on setting a strong password, please read %3$s

To pick a new password, please visit %4$s

This is an automated notification. If you would like to speak to a site administrator, please contact them directly.'=>'Pozdrav %1$s, otkriven je neuobičajeno velik broj neuspjelih pokušaja prijave na vaš račun na %2$s.

